{
  "stem": "15732.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it started a relocating us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That now was already organized from the Jewish agency.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were relocated to [INAUDIBLE] in a particular place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, part of that young people were taken-- were taken away to another place, because they hoped that they will have-- at that time, there was [SIGHS] a talk that the English government will give 100,00 certificates.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was what we call in Hebrew [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a negotiation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so they took the very young ones out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was Jewish agency already organizing, re-organizing the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- we-- Shmuelik and I, my parents, we went to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bergen-Belsen was already at that time a displaced person camp, not the concentration camp from before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a very big displaced persons camp that had a very good hospital on there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father was physically so rundown from-- from all that that we went through that he had to have medical attention.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what they-- what the-- the Jewish agency organized that we should be accepted in-- in Bergen-Belsen camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got a room there, and my father was immediately accepted to hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father was six months in Bergen-Belsen hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He went-- all sorts of injection he was given.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All sorts of-- until they habilitated him to his former self, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because of my father, in the meantime-- in the meantime, it was 1948 and it was the-- the Declaration of Independence in Israel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in Bergen-Belsen when we heard the Declaration of Independence.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did we?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did we?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I counted with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We counted with them together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We counted them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The jubilation-- jubilation at camp is not like the jubilation anywhere else, because all those people are crying and-- and laughing together.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
